N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 383-11.1 - Applicability

State Regulations

Sections 383-11.2 through
383-11.4
of this Subpart establish
the minimum requirements for surveying and marking a land disposal
facility. Notes
